# Prisma migrations live here.
#
# Migrations are GENERATED by `pnpm --filter @propulse/database migrate:dev`
# (which runs `prisma migrate dev`). Do NOT hand-write SQL migration files.
#
# Note: the Postgres Row-Level Security policies in ../rls.sql are applied as part
# of a migration (paste the contents into the generated migration's SQL, or apply
# them via a dedicated migration step) so RLS is versioned alongside the schema.
